title: War of the Roses: The Boss Won't Stop Texting Him
description: Ali is concerned because her boyfriend keeps running off to work because his boss just texted him and told him he has to come in.  After snooping around she didn't find anything suspicious from girls on his phone but she also wasn't seeing anything from his boss.  Where is he really running off to?
